code: @Override protected ListenableFuture<ClientHttpResponse> executeInternal(HttpHeaders headers, byte[] content) throws IOException {     Request request = OkHttp3ClientHttpRequestFactory.buildRequest(headers, content, this.uri, this.method).     return new OkHttpListenableFuture(this.client.newCall(request)). }
@Override public void onResponse(Call call, Response response) {     set(new OkHttp3ClientHttpResponse(response)). }
@Override public void onFailure(Call call, IOException ex) {     setException(ex). }
